# Environment Variables Setup

## Backend (.env)

```
# Database
MONGODB_URL=your_mongodb_connection_string

# Server
PORT=5000

# Email Configuration (Gmail)
EMAIL_USER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password

# JWT
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key

# Payment Gateway - Stripe
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_your_stripe_key
STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_your_stripe_key

# Payment Gateway - Razorpay
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_key_secret

# Frontend URL
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

# SMS Gateway (Optional - for production)
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your_twilio_account_sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token
TWILIO_PHONE_NUMBER=+1234567890
```

## Frontend (.env.local)

```
# API
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:5000

# Razorpay
NEXT_PUBLIC_RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id

# Stripe
NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY=pk_test_your_stripe_key
```

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Email Configuration (Gmail)
- Enable 2-factor authentication on your Gmail account
- Go to https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
- Generate an App Password
- Use this password in EMAIL_PASSWORD environment variable

### 2. Stripe Setup
- Sign up at https://dashboard.stripe.com
- Get your API keys from https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
- Use Secret Key for backend (sk_test_...)
- Use Public Key for frontend (pk_test_...)

### 3. Razorpay Setup
- Sign up at https://razorpay.com
- Get API keys from https://dashboard.razorpay.com/#/app/keys
- Key ID goes to RAZORPAY_KEY_ID
- Key Secret goes to RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET

### 4. MongoDB Setup
- Create a free cluster at https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
- Get connection string from Atlas
- Replace username and password in connection string
- Add to MONGODB_URL

### 5. JWT Secret
- Generate a secure random string:
  ```
  node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
  ```
